The Coega Development Corporation (CDC) on Tuesday said that it has, in the past couple of weeks, been made aware of social media messages that have been circulating about construction jobs that are allegedly being sold by people/persons in or outside the employ of the CDC purporting to be representing the CDC.In the brief statement, the CDC said; "The CDC views these allegations in a serious light and would like to categorically distance itself from such and to urge all those with information about this matter to contact the CDC s Tip-off Anonymous line, which is accessible via the following channels:Our readers are always advised to exercise due diligence and scrutinise every offer for employment or investment as many people have fallen victim to criminals and lost monies to scams. 